## 2. Entity Classes

We mapped the SQL design into the following JPA classes:
* [Session.java](file:///c:/TRAINING/TalentTrade/src/main/java/com/talenttrade/entity/Session.java) - Holds scheduled session data, mentor/learner relationships, times, status, and auditing timestamps.
* [Review.java](file:///c:/TRAINING/TalentTrade/src/main/java/com/talenttrade/entity/Review.java) - Maps review text and rating to a completed session.
* [Notification.java](file:///c:/TRAINING/TalentTrade/src/main/java/com/talenttrade/entity/Notification.java) - Handles DB-backed notifications for in-app messaging.

